translation[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,127,"Kananjalo uIbrâhîm noIsmâ’îl benyusa isiseko seNdlu (iKa’bha) besithi, “Nkosi yethu! Yamkela (lo msebenzi) kuthi, inene Wena Uva konke, UnguMazi weento zonke"
  2,128,"Nkosi yethu! Senze sibe ngabazithobayo kuWe (thina) nenzala yethu ibe sisizwe esikuthobelayo Wena, Usibonise kananjalo imiqathango yeHajji51, Wamkele kananjalo inguquko yethu kuba kakade nguWe Owamkela inguquko, UnguSozinceba"
  2,129,"Nkosi yethu! Bathumelele uMthunywa ongowabo52, oza kubacengcelezela iiVesi, abayalele ngokweNcwadi (i’Kur’ân) nangobulumko, Ubahlambulule, inene Wena, UnguSomandla, uSobulumko.”"
  2,130,"Ngubani na lowo ulahla inkolo kaIbrâhîm (uAbraham) ngaphandle kwalowo uzenza isidenge? Inene yena uIbrâhîm Samkhetha kweli hlabathi, yaye kuBomi oBuzayo uya kuba phakathi kwamalungisa"
  2,131,"Yabonani!Yathi iNkosiyakhe Isakuthikuye:“Zinikele(kuM)” Wathi yena, “Ndiyazinikela kwiNkosi yamaphakade”"
  2,132,"Ke kaloku oko kuzinikela kwakhe kwayalelwa nguIbrâhîm koonyana bakhe nanguYa’kûb53 (esithi), “Hini na bantwana bam! UAllâh Unikhethele inkolo (yokwenene), Ke ngoko ningaze nife ningasengawo amaMuslim”"
  2,133,"Ingaba nanikhona na ngethuba ukufa kufikela uYa’kûb? Yabonani! Wathi koonyana bakhe, “Niya kunqula bani na ndakuba ndibhubhile? Bathi bona: “Siya kunqula uThixo wakho (uAllâh), UThixo, wookhokho bakho, kaIbrâhîm, uIsmâ’îl, noIs-hâ’k,54 uThixo Omnye kwaye siya kuzinikela kuYe sibe ngamaMuslim.”"
  2,134,"Eso sisizwe esadlulayo. Baza kuvuna umvuzo woko bakusebenzelayo, nani nakuvuzwa ngoko nikwenzileyo. Aniyi kubuzwa (nto) ngoko bakwenzayo"